column3: Number of References for Principle and Subprinciples (Unique/All)

column1: * Guard Against Temptations and Distractions / Build Barriers to Avoid Bombardment (commandments - draw boundaries) (120/138)

* Don’t let it interfere with your relationship with God (25/28)
* Don’t let technology get in the way of making the Sabbath Day holy (3/4)
* Don’t let it distract from receiving truth from God (discernment) (10/11)
* Don’t let it distract you from relationships with family and others (14/16)
* Resist temptation to give into doubt and fear (3/3)
* Resist temptation to rely on things of man instead of God (2/2)
* Protect families and others from evil (21/26)
* Avoid comparison with others and be authentic (4/5)
* Live life intentionally; Prioritize better and best things (12/15)
* Technology is beneficial when used wisely (8/9)
* Technology is Rapidly Expanding Missionary Work (5/5)
* Technology has accelerated Family History and Temple Work (5/5)
